Uses of Package
sbmlme

  • Packages that use sbmlme 
    Package Description
    sbmlme
    The SBMLme package extends JSBML to encode ME-models, specifically to encode COBRAme models.
    sbmlme.converter
    The SBMLme converter package contains method for a bidirectional converter between the JSON schema of a COBRAme model and its SBMLme representation.
  • Classes in sbmlme used by sbmlme 
    Class and Description
    ElementContribution
    Implements method and attributes for creating lists of element contributions for a SubreactionData object that is a member of the list of SubreactionData in the MEProcessData.
    EnzymeInformation
    Implements method and attributes for creating and adding EnzymeInformation to SubreactionData.
    MEAbstractXMLNodePlugin
    implements basic methods for adding attributes to the XMLNode representation of the annotation of an SBML object.
    MEConstants
    Contains constants related to the SBMLme package.
    MEProcessData
    Implements methods for creating ProcessData objects for the annotation of the SBML model.
    MEReactionPlugin
    Implements attributes and methods to encode all information of reactions in a COBRAme model in SBML.
    MESpeciesPlugin
    implements attributes and methods to encode all information of species in a COBRAme model in SBML.
    MESpeciesReference
    Implements methods and attributes to create and add lists of reactants and products to SubreactionData objects and StoichiometricData objects for the MEProcessData.
    RateConstants
    Implements methods and attributes for adding rate constants to the annotation of a reaction of type "PostTranslationReaction".
    StoichiometricData
    Implements methods and attributes for encoding stoichiometric information of metabolic reactions (specifically for reactions of type "MetabolicReaction").
    SubreactionData
    Implements methods and attributes for creating SubreactionData for the list of SubreactionData and list of TranslocationData in the MEProcessData.
    SubreactionReference
    Implements methods for adding references to SubreactionData to the annotation of reactions and StoichiometricData objects.
    TranslocationReference
    Implements methods for adding references to SubreactionData of type TranslocationData to the annotation of reactions.
  • Classes in sbmlme used by sbmlme.converter 
    Class and Description
    MEConstants
    Contains constants related to the SBMLme package.
